CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 26, 1952, pg. 3 reads: "Favorite Church Woman Entries...Among the first entries in "Favorite Church Woman" contest entries are these three outstanding leaders. Left to right:...Mrs. Lucinda Harper, leader in Wesley Center AME Zion Church, Pittsburgh.  Rules governing the contest can be found elsewhere in this paper. - Harris and Sockwell Photos."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Lucinda Harper wearing light colored short sleeved blouse with circular cutouts, seated on arm of sofa with dark slipcover, another version
